**Multi-turn Strategy:**
- Turn 1: Initial survey, identify areas for investigation. Set `continue: true`.
- Turn 2+: Detailed examination using tools. Set `continue: true`.
- Penultimate turn: Call `reset()` if you used crop/zoom. Set `continue: true`.
- Final: Complete analysis with all fields in ORIGINAL image coordinates. Set `continue: false`.

